如何评价[特朗普批评加墨与美竞争2026年世界杯举办权]？

Trump的推：The U.S. has put together a STRONG bid w/ Canada & Mexico for the 2026 World Cup. It would be a shame if countries that we always support were to lobby against the U.S. bid. Why should we be supporting these countries when they don’t support us (including at the United Nations)?题主的理解：特朗普刚刚发表推文，批评加拿大、墨西哥与美国竞争2026年世界杯举办权。好吧，这英文水平，我真心醉了。。。难怪阁下这么反川啊。。。